Introduction

Jo Hyun Ah is a South Korean singer and songwriter under ABYSS Company. She is a member of the co-ed group Urban Zakapa. She studied in Howon University majoring in Practical Music. She released her first solo single, "After You", on April 18, 2018.

In 2022, she became a member of the project girl group WSG Wannabe.

She hosts a YouTube web series where she interviews celebrity guests, called Jo Hyun Ah's Thursday Night.
